-## Quick Start
+## Usage
+
+### Drop-in: Replace your SDK's partial JSON parser
+
+Every AI SDK has a `parsePartialJson` function that re-parses the full buffer on every chunk. Replace it with VectorJSON's streaming parser:

 ```js
